  [ 16] getlocal 1 .............................. <sd>
  [ 18] pusharglist 0 ........................... <>
  [ 20] extcall 388 ............................. <VOID>
  [ 23] nteq .................................... <sd <> VOID>
  [ 24] jmpifz [ 65] ............................ if sd <> VOID then
  [ 27] getlocal 1 .............................. <sd>
  [ 29] pusharglist 1 ........................... <sd>
  [ 31] extcall 912 ............................. <value(sd)>
  [ 34] setlocal 1 .............................. sd = value(sd)
  [ 36] getlocal 1 .............................. <sd>
  [ 38] pusharglist 0 ........................... <>
  [ 40] extcall 388 ............................. <VOID>
  [ 43] nteq .................................... <sd <> VOID>
  [ 44] jmpifz [ 65] ............................ if sd <> VOID then
  [ 47] getlocal 1 .............................. <sd>
  [ 49] getobjprop 1346 ......................... <sd.ver>
  [ 52] getprop 1343 ............................ <pSaveVersion>
  [ 55] eq ...................................... <sd.ver = pSaveVersion>
  [ 56] jmpifz [ 65] ............................ if sd.ver = pSaveVersion then
  [ 59] pushint8 1 .............................. <1>
  [ 61] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <1>
  [ 63] extcall 3 ............................... return 1
  [ 65] getlocal 0 .............................. <available>
  [ 67] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <available>
  [ 69] extcall 3 ............................... return available
  [ 71] ret
end

on loadGame me
