  [ 30] pusharglistnoret 0 ...................... <>
  [ 32] extcall 3 ............................... return 
  [ 34] getglobal 191 ........................... <g>
  [ 36] getchainedprop 735 ...................... <g.gamemaster>
  [ 39] pusharglist 1 ........................... <g.gamemaster>
